{"id":66,"nameArabic":"سُورَةُ التَّحۡرِيمِ","nameEnglish":"At-Tahrim","nameTranslation":"The Prohibition","revelationType":"Medinan","numberOfAyahs":12,"ayahs":[{"number":1,"arabic":"بِسْمِ ٱللَّهِ ٱلرَّحْمَٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلنَّبِىُّ لِمَ تُحَرِّمُ مَآ أَحَلَّ ٱللَّهُ لَكَ ۖ تَبْتَغِى مَرْضَاتَ أَزْوَٰجِكَ ۚ وَٱللَّهُ غَفُورٌۭ رَّحِيمٌۭ","translation":"O PROPHET! Why dost thou, out of a desire to please [one or another of] thy wives, impose [on thyself] a prohibition of something that God has made lawful to thee? But God is much-forgiving, a dispenser of grace:","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5230.mp3","surahId":66,"words":[{"id":555,"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","translation":"হে","audioUrl":"wbw/066_001_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":556,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلنَّبِىُّ","translation":"নবী","audioUrl":"wbw/066_001_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":557,"position":3,"arabic":"لِمَ","translation":"কেন","audioUrl":"wbw/066_001_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":558,"position":4,"arabic":"تُحَرِّمُ","translation":"হারাম কর তুমি","audioUrl":"wbw/066_001_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":559,"position":5,"arabic":"مَآ","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/066_001_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":560,"position":6,"arabic":"أَحَلَّ","translation":"হালাল করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/066_001_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":561,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/066_001_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":562,"position":8,"arabic":"لَكَ ۖ","translation":"তোমার জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/066_001_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":564,"position":9,"arabic":"تَبْتَغِى","translation":"তুমি চাও (কি)","audioUrl":"wbw/066_001_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":565,"position":10,"arabic":"مَرْضَاتَ","translation":"সন্তুষ্টি","audioUrl":"wbw/066_001_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":566,"position":11,"arabic":"أَزْوَٰجِكَ ۚ","translation":"তোমার স্ত্রীদের","audioUrl":"wbw/066_001_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":568,"position":12,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","translation":"এবং আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/066_001_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":569,"position":13,"arabic":"غَفُورٌۭ","translation":"ক্ষমাশীল","audioUrl":"wbw/066_001_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":570,"position":14,"arabic":"رَّحِيمٌۭ","translation":"মেহেরবান","audioUrl":"wbw/066_001_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":571,"position":15,"arabic":"١","translation":"(১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":2,"arabic":"قَدْ فَرَضَ ٱللَّهُ لَكُمْ تَحِلَّةَ أَيْمَٰنِكُمْ ۚ وَٱللَّهُ مَوْلَىٰكُمْ ۖ وَهُوَ ٱلْعَلِيمُ ٱلْحَكِيمُ","translation":"God has already enjoined upon you [O believers] the breaking and expiation of [such of] your oaths [as may run counter to what is right and just]: for, God is your Lord Supreme, and He alone is all-knowing, truly wise.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5231.mp3","surahId":66,"words":[{"id":1448,"position":1,"arabic":"قَدْ","translation":"নিশ্চয়","audioUrl":"wbw/066_002_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1449,"position":2,"arabic":"فَرَضَ","translation":"নির্দিষ্ট করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/066_002_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1450,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/066_002_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1451,"position":4,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/066_002_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1452,"position":5,"arabic":"تَحِلَّةَ","translation":"মুক্তির ব্যবস্থা","audioUrl":"wbw/066_002_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1453,"position":6,"arabic":"أَيْمَـٰنِكُمْ ۚ","translation":"তোমাদের শপথগুলোর","audioUrl":"wbw/066_002_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1455,"position":7,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","translation":"এবং আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/066_002_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1456,"position":8,"arabic":"مَوْلَىٰكُمْ ۖ","translation":"তোমাদের মনিব","audioUrl":"wbw/066_002_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1458,"position":9,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","translation":"এবং তিনিই","audioUrl":"wbw/066_002_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1459,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلْعَلِيمُ","translation":"সর্বজ্ঞ","audioUrl":"wbw/066_002_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1460,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْحَكِيمُ","translation":"প্রজ্ঞাময়","audioUrl":"wbw/066_002_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1461,"position":12,"arabic":"٢","translation":"(২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":3,"arabic":"وَإِذْ أَسَرَّ ٱلنَّبِىُّ إِلَىٰ بَعْضِ أَزْوَٰجِهِۦ حَدِيثًۭا فَلَمَّا نَبَّأَتْ بِهِۦ وَأَظْهَرَهُ ٱللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ عَرَّفَ بَعْضَهُۥ وَأَعْرَضَ عَنۢ بَعْضٍۢ ۖ فَلَمَّا نَبَّأَهَا بِهِۦ قَالَتْ مَنْ أَنۢبَأَكَ هَٰذَا ۖ قَالَ نَبَّأَنِىَ ٱلْعَلِيمُ ٱلْخَبِيرُ","translation":"And lo! [It so happened that] the Prophet told something in confidence to one of his wives; and when she thereupon divulged it, and God made this known to him, he acquainted [others] with some of it and passed over some of it. And as soon as he let her know it, she asked, \"Who has told thee this?\" - [to which] he replied, \"The All-Knowing, the All-Aware has told me.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5232.mp3","surahId":66,"words":[{"id":2493,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذْ","translation":"এবং যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/066_003_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2494,"position":2,"arabic":"أَسَرَّ","translation":"গোপনে বলেছিল","audioUrl":"wbw/066_003_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2495,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلنَّبِىُّ","translation":"নবী","audioUrl":"wbw/066_003_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2496,"position":4,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","translation":"নিকট","audioUrl":"wbw/066_003_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2497,"position":5,"arabic":"بَعْضِ","translation":"কারও","audioUrl":"wbw/066_003_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2498,"position":6,"arabic":"أَزْوَٰجِهِۦ","translation":"তার স্ত্রীদের","audioUrl":"wbw/066_003_006.mp3","charTy